        {
            "title": "LVMH股價下跌,時裝及皮革製品銷售遜於預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DkDpYjpDmIaIJWpMGtgkUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA8400B_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - LVMH酩悅·軒尼詩-路易·威登集團公佈第一季度營收為190億歐元,低於分析師預期的196億歐元,主因其關鍵的時裝及皮革製品部門表現不如預期。這家奢侈品集團有機營收增長1%,低於分析師普遍預期的1.95%,總營收按報告基準計算年減5.9%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">時裝及皮革製品是LVMH最大的業務部門,有機銷售下跌2%,而分析師預期為輕微下跌0.05%。該部門營收為92.5億歐元,年減8.5%,低於預期的94.8億歐元。公司將疲弱表現歸咎於中東衝突,該衝突對本季度有機增長造成約1%的負面影響。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b3cc71a5-f615-3832-b7ab-2ebf0b9fa7f1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">業績公佈後,LVMH美國存託憑證在紐約交易中下跌2.7%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鐘錶及珠寶成為亮點,有機營收增長7%,超過預期的4.21%。蒂芙尼(Tiffany)表現強勁,其HardWear系列增長尤為強勁。葡萄酒及烈酒部門亦表現優於預期,有機增長5%,而市場預期為下跌0.83%,主要受惠於農曆新年日曆效應對干邑銷售的有利影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">從地域來看,日本以外的亞洲地區有機增長7%,超過預期的4.2%,而美國增長3%,略高於普遍預期的2.9%。然而,歐洲下跌3%,差於預期的0.75%跌幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司表示:「LVMH在年初保持警惕但充滿信心」,強調其專注於通過持續創新和投資來發展品牌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">香水及化妝品營收有機增長持平,低於預期的1.74%增長,而精品零售增長4%,低於普遍預期的6.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/lvmh%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-%E6%99%82%E8%A3%9D%E5%8F%8A%E7%9A%AE%E9%9D%A9%E8%A3%BD%E5%93%81%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E9%81%9C%E6%96%BC%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-170754376.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-14 01:27:53",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "霍爾木茲海峽航運再度下滑 美國海上封鎖令加劇謹慎情緒",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Vessel tracking data compiled by Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zLEy6buQ8TzIaFRYxB1J3Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/dce5e20ae5cf51c04cc2d586fddcd373\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Vessel tracking data compiled by Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 霍爾木茲海峽的航運量周一再次大幅下滑，逆轉了周日的回升趨勢，市場謹慎情緒在美軍實施海上封鎖前升溫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然周日共有19艘船隻雙向通行，為戰爭初期以來最多，但這一勢頭在周一上午逆轉。周一僅觀測到4艘船隻通行：一艘液化石油氣運輸船進入海灣，三艘小型燃料油輪在紐約時間上午10點封鎖生效前數小時加速駛離。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周末一度出現油運回暖跡象，周六有三艘超級油輪通過這一全球最重要的石油通道，同時美伊在伊斯蘭堡舉行和平談判。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-088f524b-cc41-3002-bd83-530651380fd8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但在談判破裂後，美國誓言將攔截、改道或扣押離開伊朗的船隻。伊朗則警告稱，如果本國航運樞紐受到威脅，將把波斯灣及周邊所有港口都列為打擊目標。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美軍封鎖令生效 川普威脅消滅任何靠近封鎖線的伊朗船隻 (1)</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"663\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5ow6O_F758vEYEQGjx.Fng--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2Mw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e4a76d53efbecdd8e14c075bc2c8e559\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統唐納德·川普在社交媒體發文稱，周日有34艘船隻通過霍爾木茲海峽。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國實施封鎖可能促使更多船隻關閉追蹤信號以規避監測，從而使實際通行情況更難掌握。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/i7q3aD1J_ztnHQY8E3hC6A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/45965b7245976439e1286c10846c951c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Hormuz Shipping Collapses Again as US Starts Own Blockade (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\"