        {
            "title": "油市為脆弱和平定價 期權信號顯示衝突風險仍存",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/C7XPfeVSxETz0.J6_5.vow--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA5I05A_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 美國與伊朗上週宣布的臨時停火協議引發油市大幅重估,期權數據顯示投資者迅速下調但並未完全消除地緣政治風險溢價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據OptionMetrics稱,4月8日宣布停火後,\"各資產類別的風險偏好迅速反彈\",凸顯出衝突驅動的定價是多麼脆弱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">OptionMetrics首席量化分析師Garrett DeSimone表示,原油期權早已發出信號,顯示市場對持續性供應中斷持懷疑態度。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-be1b79cd-d009-3990-a032-b20d631319e9-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">即使在緊張局勢最嚴峻時,\"風險中性分佈中的大部分概率質量都遠低於遠期價格\",顯示交易員認為價格下跌是最可能的結果。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據稱OptionMetrics的分析顯示,4月7日,風險中性密度\"寬而平\",最可能的結果顯著低於當時的期貨水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這表明價格上漲是由\"概率相對較低但影響重大的右尾\"推動的,而這與局勢升級風險相關。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">停火協議宣布後,分佈急劇收緊。峰值概率上升近40%,而\"概率質量從兩端遷移回分佈主體\",反映出市場對局勢降級情境的信心增強。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據稱大幅下跌的可能性也有所減弱,左尾\"降至接近零\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,風險依然存在。OptionMetrics強調右尾持續存在\"平台期\",顯示市場仍在為一系列升級結果定價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">DeSimone表示:\"我們將當前停火協議下衝突升級的隱含概率定義為布蘭特原油結算價高於遠期價格5%以上的概率——即風險中性分佈從平滑衰減過渡到持續平台期的拐點之外的密度區域。截至4月8日,這一概率約為15-20%。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%B9%E5%B8%82%E7%82%BA%E8%84%86%E5%BC%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%9A%E5%83%B9-%E6%9C%9F%E6%AC%8A%E4%BF%A1%E8%99%9F%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E4%BB%8D%E5%AD%98-164425175.html",
